01:20:27.281 --> 01:20:28.198
Mmm.

1308
01:20:29.199 --> 01:20:31.368
- I love Mark for that.

1309
01:20:35.289 --> 01:20:36.790
Andy. hi. I'm so sorry I'm late.

1310
01:20:36.874 --> 01:20:39.376
- Oh. that's okay.

1311
01:20:39.460 --> 01:20:41.337
Stopped by that Thai place you like.

1312
01:20:42.212 --> 01:20:43.380
Want me to make you a cocktail?

1313
01:20:43.464 --> 01:20:45.966
- There she is. Hi. Hi.
- Hi.

1314
01:20:58.187 --> 01:21:00.522
Was someone a silly goose
and forget to get their roots done?

1315
01:21:00.606 --> 01:21:02.649
Mmm. Mm. Mm.

1316
01:21:02.733 --> 01:21:04.151
I got caught at the park with Cece

1317
01:21:04.234 --> 01:21:06.695
before I dropped her off
at Lena's. I'm sorry.

1318
01:21:06.779 --> 01:21:08.238
I'm gonna reschedule

1319
01:21:08.322 --> 01:21:09.823
and get this stuff on the table.

1320
01:21:09.907 --> 01:21:11.283
Hey. before you do that...

1321
01:21:12.326 --> 01:21:14.620
you think you can give me
a hand with something?

1322
01:21:17.956 --> 01:21:19.166
What?

1323
01:21:19.249 --> 01:21:21.710
I just have this last-minute meeting
with the board.

1324
01:21:21.794 --> 01:21:23.796
and there's these notes.
I cannot seem to find them.

1325
01:21:23.879 --> 01:21:25.756
I think they're upstairs
in the storage room.

1326
01:21:25.839 --> 01:21:26.840
- Right now?
- Yeah.

1327
01:21:26.924 --> 01:21:28.133
- Yeah.
- Can you give me a hand?

1328
01:21:28.634 --> 01:21:30.677
- You know it.
- Thank you.

1329
01:21:30.761 --> 01:21:33.180
Ah. I'll go turn the light on.

1330
01:21:34.681 --> 01:21:35.974
I'll be right up.

1331
01:21:36.058 --> 01:21:36.975
Okay.

1332
01:22:04.294 --> 01:22:06.130
- Babe. there's no files in here.
- I know.

1333
01:22:07.214 --> 01:22:08.132
Babe.

1334
01:22:19.393 --> 01:22:20.644
- Andy.

1335
01:22:21.478 --> 01:22:23.730
- Andy?

1336
01:22:23.814 --> 01:22:25.107
I'm here.

1337
01:22:25.190 --> 01:22:27.192
- Andy. it's locked.

1338
01:22:27.276 --> 01:22:29.236
I am very disappointed. Nina.

1339
01:22:29.319 --> 01:22:31.864
What the fuck
are you talking about?

1340
01:22:31.947 --> 01:22:36.452
Your hair is a privilege
and it needs to be cared for.

1341
01:22:38.579 --> 01:22:39.496
Um...

1342
01:22:40.831 --> 01:22:42.624
My hair?

1343
01:22:42.708 --> 01:22:44.251
Are you aware of how embarrassing it is

1344
01:22:44.334 --> 01:22:47.296
to have your wife walking around town
with her roots showing?

1345
01:22:47.379 --> 01:22:49.923
I'm gonna make another appointment.

1346
01:22:50.007 --> 01:22:51.216
I told ya.

1347
01:22:51.300 --> 01:22:53.093
I need you to be better.

1348
01:22:53.886 --> 01:22:55.804
For the both of us. I really do.

1349
01:22:55.888 --> 01:22:59.766
Andy. I'm gonna get
my fucking roots fixed. okay?

1350
01:22:59.850 --> 01:23:02.019
So you can let me out
of the room now. please.

1351
01:23:02.102 --> 01:23:04.313
I will. Just not yet.

1352
01:23:05.647 --> 01:23:08.317
I need you to understand that
there are consequences to your actions.

1353
01:23:09.151 --> 01:23:11.403
What are you fucking talking about?

1354
01:23:11.487 --> 01:23:13.989
I have an envelope.
which I will be sliding under the door.

1355
01:23:17.576 --> 01:23:19.912
Now. listen very carefully. please.

1356
01:23:19.995 --> 01:23:22.122
I need you to...

1357
01:23:22.706 --> 01:23:25.125
pluck 100 hairs

1358
01:23:25.209 --> 01:23:27.753
from your scalp with the roots intact.

1359
01:23:28.504 --> 01:23:30.047
- Um. what?
- Nina.

1360
01:23:30.130 --> 01:23:32.174
I need to see those follicles.

1361
01:23:32.257 --> 01:23:33.717
Okay. babe. you got me.

1362
01:23:33.800 --> 01:23:35.761
- That was good.

1363
01:23:37.221 --> 01:23:38.305
You got me.

1364
01:23:39.014 --> 01:23:40.307
Please let me out.

1365
01:23:40.390 --> 01:23:41.600
Once you've done that.

1366
01:23:42.392 --> 01:23:45.562
please put them back in the envelope
and slide it under the door.

1367
01:23:45.646 --> 01:23:47.439
and then we can discuss your freedom.

1368
01:23:47.523 --> 01:23:48.857
Andy!

1369
01:23:48.941 --> 01:23:50.192
This isn't funny!

1370
01:23:51.360 --> 01:23:53.237
- Andy!

1371
01:23:53.904 --> 01:23:55.239
- I'm not doing this anymore.

1372
01:23:55.322 --> 01:23:57.741
Please let me out of the fucking room!

1373
01:23:57.824 --> 01:23:59.117
I'm so sorry.

1374
01:23:59.201 --> 01:24:02.120
- Andy.

1375
01:24:02.204 --> 01:24:03.539
And I-I love you so much.

1376
01:24:04.122 --> 01:24:05.165
Babe?

1377
01:24:06.041 --> 01:24:07.167
Babe?

1378
01:24:08.710 --> 01:24:09.795
Andy?

1379
01:24:10.379 --> 01:24:12.256
Andy!

1380
01:24:12.339 --> 01:24:15.717
Cece! Andy! Please!

1381
01:24:16.301 --> 01:24:17.344
Fuck!

1382
01:24:20.764 --> 01:24:22.724
Who was this man I married?

1383
01:24:24.560 --> 01:24:26.144
What had I done

1384
01:24:26.937 --> 01:24:28.188
to deserve this?

1385
01:24:30.691 --> 01:24:31.984
No food.

1386
01:24:32.693 --> 01:24:34.820
Three tiny bottles of water.

1387
01:24:35.571 --> 01:24:38.448
The only bathroom
was a bucket in the closet.

1388
01:24:39.700 --> 01:24:42.244
I thought back to when it was
just me and you. Cece.

1389
01:24:42.327 --> 01:24:45.163
I had no idea how good we had it.

1390
01:24:48.083 --> 01:24:51.128
Even if we were constantly on the brink
of financial disaster.

1391
01:24:53.255 --> 01:24:55.173
Now what choice did I have

1392
01:24:56.049 --> 01:24:57.801
but to obey this fucker

1393
01:24:59.511 --> 01:25:01.096
if I ever wanted to see you again?

1394
01:25:51.021 --> 01:25:52.189
Andrew.

1395
01:25:53.273 --> 01:25:55.484
I did everything that you asked me to do.

1396
01:25:56.068 --> 01:25:57.653
Can you let me out. please?

1397
01:25:57.736 --> 01:26:00.238
One of the strands didn't have a follicle.

1398
01:26:00.822 --> 01:26:02.157
so you have to start again.

1399
01:26:02.240 --> 01:26:03.784
What?

1400
01:26:03.867 --> 01:26:05.410
Andrew. Andrew. please.

1401
01:26:05.494 --> 01:26:07.496
Please be more careful this time.

1402
01:26:09.665 --> 01:26:11.541
- Andrew! Please!

1403
01:26:11.625 --> 01:26:13.835
Please! Andrew. please!

1404
01:26:13.919 --> 01:26:15.837
- Andrew!

1405
01:26:28.058 --> 01:26:30.727
Oh...fuck!

1406
01:26:48.954 --> 01:26:50.539
This was for your own good.

1407
01:26:52.249 --> 01:26:53.333
If you'd let me.

1408
01:26:53.417 --> 01:26:55.252
I can help you become a better person.

1409
01:26:56.545 --> 01:26:57.671
Mmm.

1410
01:27:01.675 --> 01:27:03.218
Cece.

1411
01:27:04.720 --> 01:27:05.721
Cece!

1412
01:27:12.269 --> 01:27:15.814
Oh. baby. hi. Hi. come here. Come here.

1413
01:28:07.949 --> 01:28:08.950
Oh.

1414
01:28:26.134 --> 01:28:27.177
Cece!

1415
01:28:29.304 --> 01:28:31.473
No!

1416
01:28:31.556 --> 01:28:33.558
Cece!

1417
01:28:49.449 --> 01:28:52.118
If I were the police.
maybe I would have thought the same thing.

1418
01:28:52.202 --> 01:28:54.830
that I had drugged
and tried to drown my baby.

1419
01:28:55.622 --> 01:28:57.415
that I had swallowed a bottle of pills

1420
01:28:57.499 --> 01:28:59.417
and tried to off myself. too.

1421
01:29:06.716 --> 01:29:11.388
No one would believe
my husband was a cruel. sadistic monster.

1422
01:29:12.347 --> 01:29:14.933
How could a man that handsome.
that successful.

1423
01:29:15.016 --> 01:29:18.395
that well-loved be anything but a saint?

1424
01:29:20.313 --> 01:29:24.150
There is nothing in that attic
except boxes and papers. Nina.

1425
01:29:24.776 --> 01:29:27.571
When you're having delusions.
they can feel very real.

1426
01:29:28.405 --> 01:29:29.614
even when they're not.

1427
01:29:30.240 --> 01:29:33.493
While they pumped me
full of antipsychotics. antidepressants.

1428
01:29:34.119 --> 01:29:36.162
all I could think about was you.

1429
01:29:38.540 --> 01:29:39.708
After nine months.

1430
01:29:40.208 --> 01:29:42.210
I realized the only way to get back to you

1431
01:29:42.294 --> 01:29:43.545
was to admit...

1432
01:29:44.170 --> 01:29:46.339
what I'd done. So. I fell on my knees.

1433
01:29:47.007 --> 01:29:50.260
confessed everything
and begged for my freedom.

1434
01:29:50.844 --> 01:29:52.888
We're gonna be so happy. Nina.

1435
01:29:53.889 --> 01:29:55.849
As long as you follow the rules.

1436
01:30:35.305 --> 01:30:36.640
But by that time.

1437
01:30:37.140 --> 01:30:39.100
I understood I'd never be free.

1438
01:30:40.018 --> 01:30:43.980
No matter how hard I tried to prove
I was the happiest. most perfect wife...

1439
01:30:44.064 --> 01:30:46.232
- ...in the entire world.

1440
01:30:46.316 --> 01:30:51.821
Andrew had convinced
all those adoring shit-for-brain vipers

1441
01:30:51.905 --> 01:30:53.239
that I was crazy.

1442
01:30:53.323 --> 01:30:55.867
dangerous. unfit to raise my own daughter.

1443
01:30:55.951 --> 01:30:58.578
And he was crowned Husband of the Year

1444
01:30:58.662 --> 01:31:01.081
for sticking by his unhinged wife.

1445
01:31:02.415 --> 01:31:04.584
Of course. he wanted his own baby.

1446
01:31:04.668 --> 01:31:06.252
But there was no way

1447
01:31:06.336 --> 01:31:07.963
I was gonna let him plant

1448
01:31:08.046 --> 01:31:09.714
his evil seed in me.

1449
01:31:10.382 --> 01:31:12.717
I snuck away to the city. got an IUD.

1450
01:31:12.801 --> 01:31:16.012
the same doctor
I eventually blackmailed to lie

1451
01:31:16.096 --> 01:31:19.140
and tell Andrew
that I was fresh out of eggs.

1452
01:31:20.141 --> 01:31:22.102
Anything was an excuse to lock me up.

1453
01:31:22.686 --> 01:31:23.937
Leaving the lights on.

1454
01:31:24.020 --> 01:31:26.481
when you spilled your juice
at the breakfast table.

1455
01:31:26.564 --> 01:31:28.274
And any time I fought back.

1456
01:31:28.358 --> 01:31:32.404
he made sure to remind me
that he held all the cards.

1457
01:31:33.530 --> 01:31:36.533
Enzo was my only connection
to the outside world.

1458
01:31:36.616 --> 01:31:38.076
the only one who believed me.

1459
01:31:38.827 --> 01:31:40.745
He tried to help us escape.

1460
01:31:40.829 --> 01:31:42.288
He got us fake passports.

1461
01:31:42.372 --> 01:31:44.207
but Andrew found them in my drawer

1462
01:31:44.290 --> 01:31:46.626
and back to the institution I went.

1463
01:31:48.128 --> 01:31:49.504
Every asset was in his name.

1464
01:31:49.587 --> 01:31:52.298
I had no money. no credit.
no family. no friends.

1465
01:31:52.382 --> 01:31:54.217
I was a psych ward frequent flyer

1466
01:31:54.300 --> 01:31:56.177
with zero chance at custody.

1467
01:31:57.178 --> 01:31:58.221
If I tried to run.

1468
01:31:58.304 --> 01:32:01.391
Andrew would hunt me down
and drag us back.

1469
01:32:01.474 --> 01:32:03.560
and everyone would call him a hero.

1470
01:32:03.643 --> 01:32:05.353
I was trapped.

1471
01:32:05.437 --> 01:32:06.813
There was no chance in hell

1472
01:32:06.896 --> 01:32:09.315
he would ever let me leave
the marriage alive.

1473
01:32:09.399 --> 01:32:11.109
And if I died.

1474
01:32:11.192 --> 01:32:12.485
what would become of you?

1475
01:32:13.111 --> 01:32:15.155
What had I done

1476
01:32:15.238 --> 01:32:16.865
bringing this man

1477
01:32:16.948 --> 01:32:18.450
into your life?

1478
01:32:19.659 --> 01:32:21.161
And then it dawned on me.

1479
01:32:21.244 --> 01:32:23.288
Andrew did have a weakness.

1480
01:32:23.997 --> 01:32:25.915
his need to be adored.

1481
01:32:29.461 --> 01:32:31.755
So I started making a plan.

1482
01:32:34.716 --> 01:32:36.801
- You went away again.
- I know.

1483
01:32:37.385 --> 01:32:38.803
And now I'm back.

1484
01:32:39.512 --> 01:32:41.473
Andrew found the passports.

1485
01:32:43.808 --> 01:32:47.395
Look. I know a guy who could help.

1486
01:32:47.479 --> 01:32:49.981
I think that would only
make things worse for me.

1487
01:32:50.565 --> 01:32:51.858
I could help you.

1488
01:32:51.941 --> 01:32:53.902
You-you need to stay out of this. Enzo.

1489
01:32:53.985 --> 01:32:55.403
Listen to me carefully.

1490
01:32:56.071 --> 01:32:58.740
All right? I lost a sister
to a man like Andrew.

1491
01:32:59.324 --> 01:33:01.409
and I will not let this happen again.

1492
01:33:02.035 --> 01:33:04.287
So now you go. you pack your bag.

1493
01:33:04.788 --> 01:33:06.998
you take Cece. and you leave right now.

1494
01:33:07.082 --> 01:33:08.917
I will take care of Andrew.

1495
01:33:09.417 --> 01:33:10.335
No.

1496
01:33:11.169 --> 01:33:12.670
Andrew's gonna leave me.

1497
01:33:14.714 --> 01:33:15.757
How?

1498
01:33:19.886 --> 01:33:21.971
Millie was exactly Andrew's type.

1499
01:33:22.055 --> 01:33:25.183
Pretty. smart. blonde.

1500
01:33:25.266 --> 01:33:28.478
all alone in the world.
someone he'd want to save.

1501
01:33:29.646 --> 01:33:32.941
Disowned by her parents.
fired from her last job.

1502
01:33:33.024 --> 01:33:35.693
broke. no friends. living in her car.

1503
01:33:35.777 --> 01:33:37.278
and the crown jewel.

1504
01:33:37.362 --> 01:33:38.613
out on parole

1505
01:33:38.696 --> 01:33:41.991
after serving ten years
of a 15 year sentence.

1506
01:33:42.075 --> 01:33:44.702
And not for drugs or drunk driving

1507
01:33:44.786 --> 01:33:46.121
or some other teen bullshit.

1508
01:33:47.330 --> 01:33:49.707
She was in prison for murder.

1509
01:33:50.208 --> 01:33:53.044
My plan was to hire
a pretty girl to replace me.

1510
01:33:54.504 --> 01:33:56.548
But once I met Millie.

1511
01:33:57.173 --> 01:33:59.134
I came up with a better plan.

1512
01:34:06.182 --> 01:34:08.101
Enzo begged me to find another way.

1513
01:34:08.184 --> 01:34:10.103
to leave Millie out of all this. but...

1514
01:34:10.603 --> 01:34:13.189
I knew it was the only way
I could truly be free from Andrew.

1515
01:34:14.023 --> 01:34:16.568
I made him promise not to interfere.

1516
01:34:16.651 --> 01:34:18.736
It was her or it was Cece and me.

1517
01:34:19.487 --> 01:34:20.613
He reluctantly agreed.

1518
01:34:20.697 --> 01:34:23.366
but he said he would stay
to keep an eye on her.

1519
01:34:25.368 --> 01:34:27.412
Part of me hopes you'll never read this.

1520
01:34:27.495 --> 01:34:28.997
But if you do.

1521
01:34:29.080 --> 01:34:30.915
I'm glad you know the whole story now.

1522
01:34:31.416 --> 01:34:34.043
I just needed you to know
I wasn't a bad person.

1523
01:34:35.128 --> 01:34:38.298
Hiring Millie was the only way
I could keep you safe

1524
01:34:38.381 --> 01:34:39.632
and set us both free.

1525
01:34:39.716 --> 01:34:41.259
if we get lucky enough

1526
01:34:41.342 --> 01:34:43.428
to make it all the way to free.

1527
01:34:44.012 --> 01:34:47.265
And I figured if anyone
could take care of this situation.

1528
01:34:47.348 --> 01:34:48.266
it was her.

1529
01:35:00.820 --> 01:35:02.572
- Millie.
- Ah!

1530
01:35:02.655 --> 01:35:03.907
Millie. please stop.

1531
01:35:04.407 --> 01:35:05.325
Please?

1532
01:35:07.911 --> 01:35:08.912
Open the door.

1533
01:35:08.995 --> 01:35:10.788
- I can't do that.
- Why not? Come on.

1534
01:35:10.872 --> 01:35:12.123
I will.

1535
01:35:12.957 --> 01:35:14.000
Just not yet.

1536
01:35:15.168 --> 01:35:16.878
Andrew. what the fuck do you want?

1537
01:35:17.545 --> 01:35:19.130
It's irreplaceable. Millie.

1538
01:35:19.756 --> 01:35:20.840
What?

1539
01:35:21.424 --> 01:35:24.761
My grandmother. she brought this china
all the way from London.

1540
01:35:25.345 --> 01:35:27.222
And my mother.

1541
01:35:27.305 --> 01:35:30.350
she served every single holiday meal on it

1542
01:35:30.433 --> 01:35:32.602
with not so much as a single chip.

1543
01:35:33.436 --> 01:35:36.606
And then you drop it.

1544
01:35:37.523 --> 01:35:40.443
Like a careless child. you drop it.

1545
01:35:41.611 --> 01:35:43.279
And on top of that.

1546
01:35:43.363 --> 01:35:45.615
you don't even clean it.

1547
01:35:45.698 --> 01:35:47.742
It was an accident. Andrew.

1548
01:35:47.825 --> 01:35:50.745
Family heirlooms are a privilege. Millie.

1549
01:35:52.247 --> 01:35:54.832
And now one of mine is in 21 pieces.

1550
01:35:54.916 --> 01:35:57.752
and you didn't even clean it.

1551
01:35:58.670 --> 01:36:00.213
- Let me out.

1552
01:36:00.296 --> 01:36:01.965
you're a fucking psychopath!

1553
01:36:02.048 --> 01:36:04.592
I will let you out.
But first. you need to atone.

1554
01:36:04.676 --> 01:36:06.010
- So what you're gonna do...

1555
01:36:06.094 --> 01:36:08.346
...Is you're gonna take
this piece right here in my hand.

1556
01:36:08.429 --> 01:36:10.932
and you're gonna carve
21 lines into your stomach.

1557
01:36:11.015 --> 01:36:13.226
one for every piece
that you fucking broke.

1558
01:36:19.732 --> 01:36:20.858
Once you've done that.

1559
01:36:20.942 --> 01:36:22.860
we can discuss your freedom.

1560
01:36:22.944 --> 01:36:23.861
If...

1561
01:36:24.487 --> 01:36:25.697
you don't do it properly.

1562
01:36:25.780 --> 01:36:27.740
you are just going to have to do it again.

1563
01:36:27.824 --> 01:36:29.993
So I suggest you do it right
the first time.

1564
01:36:30.076 --> 01:36:32.120
In your fucking dreams.

1565
01:36:32.203 --> 01:36:35.665
And I need these to be long and deep cuts.

