1833
01:57:59.155 --> 01:58:00.156
Run.

1834
01:58:01.366 --> 01:58:02.367
Don't come back.

1835
01:58:03.660 --> 01:58:05.161
You didn't kill him. I did.

1836
01:58:09.749 --> 01:58:12.377
No one's gonna believe
that he fell changing a light bulb. Nina.

1837
01:58:13.878 --> 01:58:15.338
I guess we're gonna find out.

1838
01:58:17.299 --> 01:58:18.300
Go.

1839
01:58:22.971 --> 01:58:24.598
You didn't deserve any of this.

1840
01:58:27.267 --> 01:58:28.351
Neither did you.

1841
01:58:49.914 --> 01:58:52.042
Actions have consequences. Andrew.

1842
01:59:04.012 --> 01:59:05.180
Enzo. it's done.

1843
01:59:06.264 --> 01:59:08.683
I'm gonna need your help cleaning up.

1844
01:59:11.686 --> 01:59:14.022
- This must be quite a shock.

1845
01:59:15.190 --> 01:59:17.233
You said you just
returned home this evening

1846
01:59:17.317 --> 01:59:19.069
after visiting your daughter at camp.

1847
01:59:19.778 --> 01:59:21.655
And your housekeeper had the week off.

1848
01:59:21.738 --> 01:59:23.573
That's right. Yeah.

1849
01:59:24.658 --> 01:59:26.326
Do you have any idea
why your husband might have

1850
01:59:26.409 --> 01:59:28.745
decided to change a light bulb
in the middle of the night?

1851
01:59:29.412 --> 01:59:30.330
I...

1852
01:59:31.122 --> 01:59:32.165
I guess.

1853
01:59:32.666 --> 01:59:34.292
you know. well. he liked things...

1854
01:59:34.376 --> 01:59:36.378
...to be a certain way.

1855
01:59:37.045 --> 01:59:38.672
everything perfect.

1856
01:59:42.676 --> 01:59:45.095
He had quite a deep cut on his neck.

1857
01:59:48.348 --> 01:59:50.266
You don't normally see that from a fall.

1858
01:59:55.522 --> 01:59:57.482
I actually knew your husband a little bit.

1859
01:59:58.400 --> 02:00:01.027
He was engaged to my sister. Kathleen.

1860
02:00:02.862 --> 02:00:03.905
Kathy.

1861
02:00:06.074 --> 02:00:09.244
Eight years ago. she showed up
on my doorstep in the middle of the night

1862
02:00:09.327 --> 02:00:11.037
and she was never the same after that.

1863
02:00:15.542 --> 02:00:16.918
I'm sorry to hear that.

1864
02:00:19.879 --> 02:00:21.798
It must have been quite a violent fall.

1865
02:00:23.299 --> 02:00:24.342
Lots of impact.

1866
02:00:25.760 --> 02:00:26.928
Skin breaks.

1867
02:00:28.388 --> 02:00:29.431
Bones break.

1868
02:00:32.308 --> 02:00:33.309
Teeth break.

1869
02:00:44.529 --> 02:00:47.824
It seems to me this is just
one of those freak household accidents.

1870
02:00:50.910 --> 02:00:53.413
Sometimes bad things happen
to good people.

1871
02:01:09.304 --> 02:01:12.557
We gather here today
to mourn the tragic passing

1872
02:01:12.640 --> 02:01:14.350
of Andrew Winchester.

1873
02:01:15.769 --> 02:01:17.103
Devoted son.

1874
02:01:17.187 --> 02:01:19.773
dedicated husband and father.

1875
02:01:19.856 --> 02:01:21.900
a respected business leader.

1876
02:01:22.692 --> 02:01:25.195
and true pillar of the community.

1877
02:01:25.779 --> 02:01:27.947
His untimely death has left us all

1878
02:01:28.031 --> 02:01:29.741
with a sense of shock.

1879
02:01:29.824 --> 02:01:32.285
that such a vital and caring man could

1880
02:01:32.368 --> 02:01:34.078
suddenly be taken from us.

1881
02:01:34.621 --> 02:01:39.334
We struggle in these times
to understand God's plan.

1882
02:01:40.460 --> 02:01:43.922
and it is natural to question
God's power in times of grief.

1883
02:01:45.715 --> 02:01:48.426
But we must never lose our faith

1884
02:01:49.010 --> 02:01:51.429
- in God's love.
- Hi. Thank you for coming.

1885
02:01:51.513 --> 02:01:52.764
Thank you.

1886
02:01:53.807 --> 02:01:56.434
- Hi.
- Nina.

1887
02:01:56.518 --> 02:01:57.936
I'm so sorry.

1888
02:01:59.103 --> 02:02:01.606
Now. are you sure
you're still gonna sell the house?

1889
02:02:01.689 --> 02:02:04.317
What are you gonna do with yourselves
all the way out in California?

1890
02:02:04.400 --> 02:02:06.486
Oh. well. I think we'll manage.

1891
02:02:07.195 --> 02:02:09.280
I'm so sorry about your son.

1892
02:02:09.781 --> 02:02:11.241
What a terrible accident.

1893
02:02:11.991 --> 02:02:13.827
He had a beautiful smile.

1894
02:02:13.910 --> 02:02:15.495
- didn't he?
- The best.

1895
02:02:15.578 --> 02:02:18.122
You know. they told me
he was missing a tooth

1896
02:02:18.957 --> 02:02:20.124
when they found him.

1897
02:02:20.959 --> 02:02:22.710
- Oh. my God.
- My God.

1898
02:02:22.794 --> 02:02:24.295
Yeah. Did you know that?

1899
02:02:24.379 --> 02:02:26.214
- Hmm.
- Did you?

1900
02:02:26.798 --> 02:02:28.508
That a tooth was gone?

1901
02:02:32.136 --> 02:02:33.930
If you don't take care of your teeth.

1902
02:02:34.013 --> 02:02:36.140
you lose the privilege of having them.

1903
02:02:37.141 --> 02:02:39.060
because teeth...

1904
02:02:40.478 --> 02:02:41.813
are a privilege.

1905
02:02:44.315 --> 02:02:47.110
- My condolences.
- Take good care.

1906
02:02:51.656 --> 02:02:53.366
This is how you allow her to dress

1907
02:02:53.449 --> 02:02:54.993
for her father's funeral?

1908
02:02:57.370 --> 02:02:58.621
Hey.

1909
02:03:04.502 --> 02:03:05.545
Excuse me.

1910
02:03:25.565 --> 02:03:26.649
I told you to run.

1911
02:03:27.233 --> 02:03:28.234
I can't run.

1912
02:03:29.193 --> 02:03:30.653
I'm on parole. Remember?

1913
02:03:44.542 --> 02:03:46.336
Just make a life for yourself.

1914
02:04:11.903 --> 02:04:14.739
Wow. Well. tell me about yourself. Millie.

1915
02:04:15.907 --> 02:04:18.743
Well. I definitely didn't plan
on being a housemaid.

1916
02:04:19.327 --> 02:04:21.287
It sort of just fell into my lap.

1917
02:04:21.371 --> 02:04:23.831
and I realized I really enjoy it.

1918
02:04:24.666 --> 02:04:26.501
For the right families. of course.

1919
02:04:26.584 --> 02:04:29.295
Nina Winchester
recommended you very highly.

1920
02:04:30.254 --> 02:04:31.255
She...

1921
02:04:32.966 --> 02:04:35.760
She suggested you. actually.

1922
02:04:36.594 --> 02:04:38.930
Mrs. Winchester
was a pleasure to work for.

1923
02:04:41.057 --> 02:04:42.058
I...

1924
02:04:45.019 --> 02:04:46.562
I have to warn you.

1925
02:04:49.023 --> 02:04:51.776
My husband is a...

1926
02:04:53.361 --> 02:04:55.238
hard man to please.

1927
02:05:00.410 --> 02:05:01.953
So do you think you can help?

1928
02:05:04.247 --> 02:05:05.873
When would you like me to start?
